  "informal_statement": "The squared distance expands into the standard quadratic form.",
  "informal_proof_idea": "Expand the binomial squares; `ring`.",
  "formal_statement_pp": "theorem distance_expand (x1 y1 x2 y2 : ℝ) : (x2 - x1) ^ 2 + (y2 - y1) ^ 2 = x2 ^ 2 - 2 * x1 * x2 + x1 ^ 2 + (y2 ^ 2 - 2 * y1 * y2 + y1 ^ 2)",
